  "detailed_description": "Rodland of Pipes is a game about crawling through pipes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/d0ef50f1f9af1de6759ef6a04e6d353a.poster.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/d0ef50f1f9af1de6759ef6a04e6d353a.webm?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/d0ef50f1f9af1de6759ef6a04e6d353a.mp4?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The pipes are cramped, making turning around impossible. Plan a route if you want to make it out in time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/a89be18d191fa8846bdd03253548b4c9.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>You’re not alone down here, don’t let yourself become an easy meal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/87271fa6983d3cab7954c20f108d84cd.poster.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/87271fa6983d3cab7954c20f108d84cd.webm?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/87271fa6983d3cab7954c20f108d84cd.mp4?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But just who is Rodland? Is he really running a small plumbing business or is something more sinister in motion?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/4bc60e2aeba7ea2dcf1f8f8c79e9412d.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>A colorful cast of pipe denizens to discover. Each with unique AI, mechanics, and a hand animated jumpscare.<br>Randomized elements, every journey into the pipes is unique<br>Adjustable difficulty<br>Rich immersive audio<br>Secrets!<br>Custom level editor<br>An estimated 3-4 hours for a full playthrough<br>A song at the very end",
  "about_the_game": "Rodland of Pipes is a game about crawling through pipes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/d0ef50f1f9af1de6759ef6a04e6d353a.poster.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/d0ef50f1f9af1de6759ef6a04e6d353a.webm?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/d0ef50f1f9af1de6759ef6a04e6d353a.mp4?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The pipes are cramped, making turning around impossible. Plan a route if you want to make it out in time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/a89be18d191fa8846bdd03253548b4c9.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>You’re not alone down here, don’t let yourself become an easy meal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/87271fa6983d3cab7954c20f108d84cd.poster.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/87271fa6983d3cab7954c20f108d84cd.webm?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/87271fa6983d3cab7954c20f108d84cd.mp4?t=1725319927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But just who is Rodland? Is he really running a small plumbing business or is something more sinister in motion?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125120/extras/4bc60e2aeba7ea2dcf1f8f8c79e9412d.avif?t=1725319927\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>A colorful cast of pipe denizens to discover. Each with unique AI, mechanics, and a hand animated jumpscare.<br>Randomized elements, every journey into the pipes is unique<br>Adjustable difficulty<br>Rich immersive audio<br>Secrets!<br>Custom level editor<br>An estimated 3-4 hours for a full playthrough<br>A song at the very end",
